<div
	class="box-border flex h-full min-h-0 flex-col overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden bg-page p-8 text-ink"
	style="min-height: 100%; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;"
>
	<p class="font-sans text-[10px] font-medium tracking-[0.25em] text-muted uppercase">
		In her words
	</p>
	<h2 class="font-display mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
		A quick chat
	</h2>

	<div class="mt-6 space-y-6 font-sans">
		<div class="space-y-2">
			<p class="text-left text-sm font-bold leading-snug text-ink">
				What first drew you to modeling—and what keeps you motivated?
			</p>
			<blockquote class="m-0 border-0 p-0 text-left text-xs leading-relaxed text-ink/90">
				<span class="font-serif text-[1.05em] text-ink/70">“</span>I’ve been interested in modeling since my early teens, and now I’m slowly exploring it as something I genuinely enjoy. I love being on the runway and doing photoshoots—it feels natural and fun for me, and I’m excited to keep growing, gaining more experience, and seeing where this journey takes me.<span class="font-serif text-[1.05em] text-ink/70">”</span>
			</blockquote>
		</div>
		<div class="space-y-2">
			<p class="text-left text-sm font-bold leading-snug text-ink">
				Which kind of modeling do you love most—and what do you want to explore more in the future?
			</p>
			<blockquote class="m-0 border-0 p-0 text-left text-xs leading-relaxed text-ink/90">
				<span class="font-serif text-[1.05em] text-ink/70">“</span>I like the feeling of walking the runway so much—it makes me feel confident and in control. All the preparation and wardrobes… I just love it! I’m also a huge fan of photoshoots because I love being in front of the lens and experimenting with poses.<span class="font-serif text-[1.05em] text-ink/70">”</span>
			</blockquote>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
